Anon posting about daughterfur Krystal in the thread before had me reminiscing. Back when I used to do dream induction techniques to conjure furries, it never really worked as intended, anyway, I did get an instance where a younger Krystal was present. It was a little jarring, I'd call it, I suppose because I've always thought of her as being older than me. There was a base, or research facility, for rockets and starfighters and combat mechs and so on, along with these enclosures for alien wildlife. Had the distinctive feel of a less fucked version of the original black mesa. And Krystalmom existed as one of the scientists, there were lots of scientists with families and children in this place, in fact.
Krystal was different here of course, she was kind of irritable and moody, not disciplined. Which is what you'd expect I guess. No reason to assume anthro girls would be too different on average from human ones.

The mind reading shenanigans would be interesting, I suppose. A unique problem (sometimes?) you'd have to deal with.
